data.description: Step into your dream home nestled in charming and historic Salado, TX! This remarkable property boasts over 1 acre of land, featuring a captivating view of 58 acre agricultural fields from its expansive covered front porch. The main residence encompasses 3 bedrooms, 2 full baths, a half bath, 2 spacious living areas, dining room, and a home office. Additionally, a guest quarters with convenient wet bar and half bath is accessible through a separate entrance off the back patio. For those seeking versatile workspace, a metal building/workshop, constructed in 2022, offers 864 sq ft of space complete with an office and half bath. Recent updates, undertaken since 2021, include fresh paint throughout, elegant wood flooring throughout, updated primary suite, modernized light fixtures and ceiling fans, a new dishwasher, built-in microwave, and a roof replacement in 2023 with dent-resistant shingles. This property is truly a must-see gem, blending charm, functionality, and comfort in a picturesque setting! Schedule your tour immediately.
